Refers to any original work of authorship or derivative work covered by this License, including but not limited to software source code, scripts, documentation, artwork, and other creative outputs.

“Contributor”
Any individual or legal entity that authors or contributes to the Work. A Contributor may include, but is not limited to, original authors, maintainers, and those who submit modifications or additions to the Work.

“Contribution”
Any change, addition, or improvement to the Work that is intentionally submitted by a Contributor for inclusion in the Work. This includes, but is not limited to, source code, documentation, and supporting resources.

“User”
